dct_description_sm: Covers the southern portions of British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan, and Manitoba.; Relief shown by spot heights.; Also shows locations of branches of the bank with red stars overprinted on the map.; "Presented with the compliments of The Canadian Bank of Commerce."; "Copies of this map may be had on application to any Branch of The Canadian Bank of Commerce."; List of cities and towns in which exist "Branches of The Canadian Bank of Commerce situated in Western Canada" on verso.
